(368, '2014-12-15', 600015686, 2014, 5, 'b', '                                          \r\n  Long time ago, human bing were started with hunting and searching for their food. Then they developing a new ways to cover their nutritional requirments through inplantations and domesticated the animals. But this development did not stop and growing of the farms become a competation for  the people. Covering of the food requirment were rosen to be a souce of collacting money ,so now ady the farm become a copmuny to increase the amount of the products and the quality of the food.But do we need more?And do this factory fit for all communties?\r\n        The combination between the two words factory and farming is refering to one thing which is harvest of the money. Today  this industries become one of the main soruces of the food products According to Fisher David in "Factory Farming" According to Worldwatch, factory farms are the source of 74 percent of the world''s poultry, 68 percent of egg, 50 percent of pork, and 43 percent of beef." (David) these number are giving an indecation to the size of the invesment of these industries. The amont of their prodcuts and the comptetion between these factories  lead to decline of the prices and it''s become more available. Furthermore David states that the viral growing in the products of this farm increased the consumption of the meat more than the past. \r\n      Onthe other hand, according to the Berlin james in " industtrial farming Theatens the Third World" " When factory farming corporations move into a developing, It can destroy traditional farming methods and threaten local animal breeds. bringing more insread of less poverty to poor nations"most of  the farming factories have a great investment and some of them have many branch in diffrent palces, and with this size of investment small farmers do not have any apportunity to make their works,so the final rersults for those people is lossing the source of their income and tre