the government provide them with machines enable them to gain a lot of benefits in few period. This is conseder one of the method to encourage farmer to work more and more. \n            In the past,many people are unable to have agood income even they work over- time, but now many people are able to eat meat, vegetable,grain crops, and fruit, because the cost of those things are less than before. Moreover people can eat many kinds of fruit and vegetable from many places around the world. Exportation and inportations one of the charchterestic evidance to improve the wealthy of people. If the consumer is unable to buy those inported crops, there will be no need to inport them,as well as if there is no over left of the crops, there will be no export. providing enough food to the whole population  are aid by modren farming techniques (Fisher "Factory Farming") The number of population are increased over and over and need a hug amount of food to be able to survive, to tell the tale, hunger is the real threaten to human being and the solution is industrial farming. For instance, when Iraq suffered from punshment arter the Gulf war, people only were thinking about peoviding food to their children. People stop thinking about anything alse, like education or clothing or anymaterial because they were unable to provide the food to their children. thinking of hunger and death is the major threatens arounf the global.  \n          In sum, using invention is the only way to prevent hunger around the global. If the farmer has agood benefit from his work, it will encourage him to work more and more. Futhermore, people income is very low which make them suffer from hunger if they wold not get suitable prise for their food. Advantages of the factory farming is over weight its disadvantages and makes it win the race. Helping human to increase their life class is by providing them with enough food.avoid the dangerous of industeres ', '00:00:00', '2.0', '2.0', '2.5', '2.0', '2.0', '10.